title: [Ta'Illistim, Mzaarine Bazaar]
description: Vibrant silk awnings project from cozy ivied buildings, nestled away from the cobblestone bazaar.  Tree-lined walkways pass through florid gardens leading to their closed doors.  The air is perfumed with the delightful blend of freesia and roses.
